# XStudio Global Rules
[type]: Always
- React 19 + TypeScript 5 + RAC + Zustand + Tailwind v4 + Supabase
- **No inline Tailwind** in .tsx; use tv() + semantic CSS classes
- **No @apply** in CSS (Tailwind v4 금지); use @layer + CSS variables
- **Inspector**: Inline styles (React style prop) + computed styles from Preview
- **Preview**: Collects computed styles via getComputedStyle() + postMessage
- **PIXI**: No x/y props; use style-based layout (@pixi/layout)
- Supabase: RLS + service modules + hooks; no secrets in client
- postMessage origin validation; queue until PREVIEW_READY
- **History**: Record before state mutation (Undo/Redo support)
- **O(1) Lookup**: Use elementsMap/childrenMap, not array.find()
- CSS variables for theming (--builder-*, --action-*)
